{"tid":1280652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】 貨幣逃出戰","createTime":"2019-07-03T04:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T05:02:36.000Z","uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"81f497a9b88163223292451261f3e6c0e7eb038a","tid":1280652,"uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"以前大家都知道有線有幾難cut<br />\n而家有一個差唔多咁難拎錢嘅銀行<br />\n睇下大家可唔可以集思廣益點樣拎到錢走<br />\n我諗咗幾個方法唔知有冇用<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n冇馬會account嘅開馬會account<br />\n記得要問職員拎智財卡<br />\nset 中銀自動轉帳<br />\n每日最多可以用張卡拎幾萬出嚟<br />\n2.<br />\n親自殺上去銀行 <br />\n好似當年cut有線嗰個痴線佬咁樣<br />\n順手嘈下啲職員 降低佢哋工作士氣<br />\n3.<br />\n轉數快 不過本身我唔用中銀 <br />\n唔知有冇手續費"},{"pid":"079c88fd62106f99d22ea56a02add83cb2453ca6","tid":1280652,"uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"大家有冇其他方法 可以拎到嚿錢出嚟"},{"pid":"e5a3a871352cfc3f0e68f6d8d14aac5a2b4234aa","tid":1280652,"uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KHEY3P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KHEY3P.jpg&h=9c91f7d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cfe4qJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCfe4qJQ.jpg&h=2589d490&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}